{"id":"tool-proverka-subsidii","type":["tool"],"name":"Проверка субсидии","aliases":[],"summary":"Мастер определяет режим вашей субсидии или гранта: нужен ли лицевой счёт и Сведения, кто утверждает расходы, какая отчётность и когда возникает риск возврата. Субсидии контролируются строже контрактов: нарушение целей или отчётности ведёт к возврату всей суммы с неустойкой.","citation":"Вход: стадия и тип субсидии. Выход: карта обязанностей получателя + риски.","pages":[{"layer":"tool","url":"/instrumenty/proverka-subsidii/","title":"Проверка субсидии"}],"relations":{"USES_TERM":["subsidiya","soglashenie-subsidii","poluchatel-subsidii","id-soglasheniya","svedeniya-ssu","tselevye-sredstva","err-necelevoe","otchet-subsidii","neisp-ostatok"],"SEE_FAQ":["faq-subsidiya-pod-ks","faq-vozvrat-subsidii","faq-otchet-po-subsidii","faq-raskhody-subsidii","faq-svedeniya-po-subsidii","faq-ufk-ne-soglasuet-subsidiyu","faq-razdelenie-subsidii-i-svoih","faq-nedostizhenie-pokazateley","faq-ostatok-subsidii"],"PART_OF_TOPIC":["hub-subsidii"],"REGULATED_BY":["law-bk-rf-st-2422224226","law-ezhegodnyy-zakon-o-federalnom-byudzhete","law-koap-rf-st-1514"],"EXPLAINED_BY_ARTICLE":["/blog/kaznacheyskoe-soprovozhdenie-subsidiy-2026"],"REQUIRES_DOC":["komplekt-subsidii","svedeniya-ssu","poyasnenie-ufk","zayavlenie-zakrytie"],"PREVENTS":["err-subsidiya-rashody","err-necelevoe"],"RESOLVES_TO":["service-conduct","service-vosstanovlenie"]},"updated":"2026-07-09","schema_id":"https://kazna-gov.ru/#e-tool-proverka-subsidii","scores":{"authority":1,"coverage":100,"connectivity":100,"citation":80,"aiReadiness":100,"density":100}}